From 3583791edd712abbc2c4066a9ab18813cf4d8aa0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Thiraviyam Mariyappan <tmariyap@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 7 May 2025 23:05:30 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] UPSTREAM:DP:ath12k: Enable RAW MODE set bit flag

This patch enables the RAW mode set bit flag for RAW mode data transfer.

Original Patch:
000-d-Revert-wifi-ath12k-remove-unused-frame_mode-module-p.patch

Signed-off-by: Thiraviyam Mariyappan <tmariyap@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/core.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/core.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/core.c
@@ -1247,6 +1247,9 @@ static int ath12k_core_hw_group_start(st
 		return -EINVAL;
 	}
 
+	if (ath12k_frame_mode == ATH12K_HW_TXRX_RAW)
+		set_bit(ATH12K_GROUP_FLAG_RAW_MODE, &ag->flags);
+
 	ret = ath12k_mac_allocate(ag);
 	if (WARN_ON(ret))
 		return ret;
